ine text"], "original_format": ["newspaper"], "other_formats": [{"label": "MODSXML Record", "link": "//tile.loc.gov/storage-services/service/ndnp//iahi/batch_iahi_jackson_ver01/data/sn86061215/00415668764/1908051201/1908051201_1.xml"}, {"label": "MARCXML Record", "link": "//lccn.loc.gov/sn86061215/marcxml"}], "other_title": ["Tri-weekly courier", "Ottumwa courier"], "partof": [{"count": 2003, "title": "ottumwa tri-weekly courier (ottumwa, iowa) 1903-1916", "url": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=partof:ottumwa+tri-weekly+courier+%28ottumwa,+iowa%29+1903-1916&fo=json"}, {"count": 3203926, "title": "chronicling america", "url": "https://www.loc.gov/collections/chronicling-america/?fo=json"}, {"count": 3225157, "title": "serial and government publications division", "url": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=partof:serial+and+government+publications+division&fo=json"}], "partof_collection": ["chronicling america"], "partof_division": ["serial and government publications division"], "partof_title": ["ottumwa tri-weekly courier (ottumwa, iowa) 1903-1916"], "place_of_publication": "Ottumwa, Iowa", "publication_frequency": ["triweekly"], "raw_lccn": "sn 86061215 ", "reel_numbers": ["00415668764"], "resources": [{"files": 10, "image": "https://tile.loc.gov/image-services/iiif/service:ndnp:iahi:batch_iahi_jackson_ver01:data:sn86061215:00415668764:1908051201:1035/full/pct:3.125/0/default.jpg", "url": "https://www.loc.gov/resource/sn86061215/1908-05-12/ed-1/", "word_coordinates": "https://tile.loc.gov/text-services/word-coordinates-service"}], "rights": ["<p>The Library of Congress believes that the newspapers in Chronicling America are in the public domain or have no known copyright restrictions.  Newspapers published in the United States more than 95 years ago are in the public domain in their entirety. Any newspapers in Chronicling America that were published less than 95 years ago are also believed to be in the public domain, but may contain some copyrighted third party materials. Researchers using newspapers published less than 95 years ago should be alert for modern content (for example, registered and renewed for copyright and published with notice) that may be copyrighted.  Responsibility for making an independent legal assessment of an item and securing any necessary permissions ultimately rests with persons desiring to use the item.</p>\n<p>The NEH awardee responsible for producing each digital object is presented in the Chronicling America page display, below the page image  \u2013 e.g. Image produced by the Library of Congress. For more information on current NDNP awardees, see <a href=\"https://www.loc.gov/ndnp/listawardees.html\">https://www.loc.gov/ndnp/listawardees.html</a>.</p>\n<p>For more information on Library of Congress policies and disclaimers regarding rights and reproductions, see <a href=\"https://www.loc.gov/homepage/legal.html\">https://www.loc.gov/homepage/legal.html</a></p>"], "score": 14.141635, "shard": "05", "shelf_id": "sn86061215, 1908-05-12, Edition 1", "site": ["chroniclingamerica"], "source_group": "ndnp/iahi", "source_modified": "2000-01-01T12:00:00Z", "subject": ["ottumwa", "newspapers", "united states", "ottumwa (iowa)", "wapello", "iowa"], "subject_headings": ["Ottumwa (Iowa)--Newspapers", "Iowa--Ottumwa", "United States--Iowa--Wapello--Ottumwa"], "subjects": [{"iowa": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=subject:iowa&fo=json"}, {"newspapers": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=subject:newspapers&fo=json"}, {"ottumwa": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=subject:ottumwa&fo=json"}, {"ottumwa (iowa)": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=subject:ottumwa+%28iowa%29&fo=json"}, {"united states": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=subject:united+states&fo=json"}, {"wapello": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=subject:wapello&fo=json"}], "timestamp": "2023-07-04T07:45:59.536Z", "title": "Ottumwa tri-weekly courier (Ottumwa, Iowa), May 12, 1908", "type": ["issue"], "url": "https://www.loc.gov/item/sn86061215/1908-05-12/ed-1/"}, "locations": null, "method": "mets_filesec", "more_like_this": [{"access_restricted": false, "aka": ["http://www.loc.gov/item/sn86061215/", "http://lccn.loc.gov/sn86061215"], "batch": ["iahi_grimes_ver01"], "campaigns": [], "date": "1903", "description": ["Triweekly Vol. 55, no. 59 (Oct. 20, 1903)-v. 69, no. 21 (Sept. 26, 1916). Archived issues are available in digital format from the Library of Congress Chronicling America online collection. Ottumwa semi-weekly courier (1916) 2375-3250 (DLC)sn 86061216 (OCoLC)14942033"], "digitized": true, "extract_timestamp": "2026-06-05T18:25:11.942Z", "group": ["newspaper-titles", "ndnp/newspapers", "catalog-split-14", "catalog", "united-states-newspaper-directory", "main-catalog-split-14"], "hassegments": false, "id": "http://www.loc.gov/item/sn86061215/", "image_url": [], "index": 1, "language": ["english"], "latlong": [41.0232527, -92.4132637], "location": ["iowa", "wapello", "ottumwa", "united states"], "location_str": "", "lonlat": [-92.4132637, 41.0232527], "number": ["sn86061216", "1", "2002", "14941985", "sn86061214", "crest microfilm, collection 1", "2024-05-12t17:17:02.191186", "new york state - vx6", "microfilm master", "2375-3285", "sn84027330", "microfilm service copy", "online resource", "original", "sn86061215", "2025-06-25t14:23:53", "http://www.loc.gov/item/sn86061215/1916-09-26/ed-1/", "http://www.loc.gov/item/sn86061215/1903-10-20/ed-1/", "2026-04-13t21:30:13", "state hist soc of iowa, newspaper off"], "original_format": ["newspaper"], "other_title": ["Tri-weekly courier", "Ottumwa courier"], "partof": ["serial and government publications division", "chronicling america", "catalog", "ottumwa tri-weekly courier (ottumwa, iowa) 1903-1916", "directory of u.s. newspapers in american libraries"], "publication_frequency": ["triweekly"], "score": 59.8696, "shelf_id": "Newspaper", "site": ["chroniclingamerica", "usnd", "catalog"], "subject": ["ottumwa", "newspapers", "united states", "ottumwa (iowa)", "wapello", "iowa"], "timestamp": "2026-07-18T09:18:25.078Z", "title": "Ottumwa tri-weekly courier", "type": ["title"], "url": "https://www.loc.gov/item/sn86061215/"}, {"access_restricted": false, "aka": ["http://www.loc.gov/item/2018218662/"], "campaigns": [], "date": "1848", "dates": ["[1848 TO 1854]"], "description": ["Weekly Began August 8, 1848; ceased June 15, 1854. Publisher varies. \"Devoted to politics, general news, literature, agriculture, mechanics, education, markets, etc.\" Issues for <Nov. 2, 1849>-Jan. 5, 1854 called also whole no. <58>-260; issues for Jan. 12-June 15, 1854 lack numbering; no issue published June 8,1854. Description based on: Volume 2, no. 7, whole no. 59 (November 9, 1849); title from masthead (Chroniclingamerica.loc.gov, viewed March 28, 2018). Latest issue consulted: June 15, 1854 (Chroniclingamerica.loc.gov, viewed March 28, 2018). Demoine courier (DLC) 2018218663"], "digitized": true, "extract_timestamp": "2026-05-19T21:37:42.357Z", "group": ["ndnp/newspapers", "united-states-newspaper-directory"], "hassegments": false, "id": "http://www.loc.gov/item/2018218662/", "image_url": [], "index": 2, "language": ["english"], "location": ["iowa", "wapello", "ottumwa", "united states"], "number": ["online resource", "2577-4123", "2018218663", "1029739115", "2018218662", "2026-04-13t21:30:13"], "original_format": ["newspaper"], "other_title": ["Courier"], "partof": ["serial and government publications division", "des moines courier (ottumwa, iowa) 1848-1854 [online resource]", "directory of u.s. newspapers in american libraries"], "publication_frequency": ["weekly"], "score": 50.694965, "shelf_id": "ISSN RECORD", "site": ["usnd"], "subject": ["ottumwa", "newspapers", "united states", "ottumwa (iowa)", "wapello", "iowa"], "timestamp": "2026-05-26T20:56:09.337Z", "title": "Des Moines courier", "type": ["title"], "url": "https://www.loc.gov/item/2018218662/"}, {"access_restricted": false, "aka": ["http://www.loc.gov/item/2018218663/"], "campaigns": [], "date": "1854", "dates": ["[1854 TO 1856]"], "description": ["Weekly Began with vol. 6, no. 23, whole no. 283 (June 22, 1854); ceased with vol. 8, no. 43 (December 25, 1856). Publisher varies: J. W. Norris, December 20, 1855-December 25, 1856. Issues for June 22-Aug. 17, 1854 called also whole no. 283-291. Description based on: Vol. 6, no. 23, whole no. 283 (June 22, 1854); title from masthead (Chroniclingamerica.loc.gov, viewed March 28, 2018). Latest issue consulted: Vol. 8, no. 43 (December 25, 1856) (Chroniclingamerica.loc.gov, viewed March 28, 2018). Weekly Ottumwa courier (DLC) 2018218664"], "digitized": true, "extract_timestamp": "2026-05-19T21:37:42.357Z", "group": ["ndnp/newspapers", "united-states-newspaper-directory"], "hassegments": false, "id": "http://www.loc.gov/item/2018218663/", "image_url": [], "index": 3, "language": ["english"], "location": ["iowa", "wapello", "ottumwa", "united states"], "number": ["online resource", "1029739653", "2018218664", "2018218663", "2577-414x", "2018218662", "2026-04-13t21:30:13"], "original_format": ["newspaper"], "partof": ["serial and government publications division", "directory of u.s. newspapers in american libraries", "demoine courier (ottumwa, iowa) 1854-1856 [online resource]"], "publication_frequency": ["weekly"], "score": 50.694965, "shelf_id": "ISSN RECORD", "site": ["usnd"], "subject": ["ottumwa", "newspapers", "united states", "ottumwa (iowa)", "wapello", "iowa"], "timestamp": "2026-05-26T20:56:09.337Z", "title": "Demoine courier", "type": ["title"], "url": "https://www.loc.gov/item/2018218663/"}, {"access_restricted": false, "aka": ["http://www.loc.gov/item/2018218664/"], "campaigns": [], "date": "1857", "dates": ["[1857 TO 1872]"], "description": ["Weekly Beganwith new series, vol. 2, no. 1=old series, vol. 8, no. 44 (January 1, 1857); ceased with vol. 24, no. 32 (Nov. 21, 1872). \"Weekly\" appears above title ornament, Jan. 23, 1868-Nov. 21, 1872. Publisher varies. Issues for Jan. 1, 1857-<Jan. 7, 1864> called also new ser., v. 2, no. 1-<v. 8, no. 51>. \"Courier extra\" published May 12, 1869. Description based on: New series, vol. 2, no. 1=old series, vol. 8, no. 44 (January 1, 1857); title from masthead (Chroniclingamerica.loc.gov, viewed March 28, 2018). Latest issue consulted: New series, vol. 11, no. 18=old series, vol. 18, no. 10 (May 31, 1866) (Chroniclingamerica.loc.gov, viewed March 28, 2018). Ottumwa weekly courier 2643-6582 (DLC) 2019271096 (OCoLC)1100481615"], "digitized": true, "extract_timestamp": "2026-05-19T21:37:42.357Z", "group": ["ndnp/newspapers", "united-states-newspaper-directory"], "hassegments": false, "id": "http://www.loc.gov/item/2018218664/", "image_url": [], "index": 4, "language": ["english"], "location": ["iowa", "wapello", "ottumwa", "united states"], "number": ["online resource", "2018218664", "2019271096", "2018218663", "1029740077", "2577-4174", "2026-04-13t21:30:13"], "original_format": ["newspaper"], "other_title": ["Ottumwa weekly courier", "Ottumwa courier", "Weekly courier"], "partof": ["serial and government publications division", "directory of u.s. newspapers in american libraries", "the weekly ottumwa courier (ottumwa, iowa) 1857-1872 [online resource]"], "publication_frequency": ["weekly"], "score": 50.694965, "shelf_id": "ISSN RECORD", "site": ["usnd"], "subject": ["ottumwa", "newspapers", "united states", "ottumwa (iowa)", "wapello", "iowa"], "timestamp": "2026-05-26T20:56:09.337Z", "title": "The weekly Ottumwa courier", "type": ["title"], "url": "https://www.loc.gov/item/2018218664/"}, {"access_restricted": false, "aka": ["http://www.loc.gov/item/2019271096/"], "campaigns": [], "date": "1872", "dates": ["[1872 TO 1899]"], "description": ["Semiweekly, Nov. 4, 1890-July 27, 1899 Began with volume 24, number 33 (November 28, 1872); ceased v. 51, no. 36 (July 27, 1899). Second part of July 27, 1899 issue published as: Ottumwa semi-weekly courier. Weekly issues published in two parts, twice a week, Nov. 4, 1890-July 27, 1899. Des